description:
This is a 6 minute workout called '5 Minute Breathing Exercise - Guided Mindfulness Meditation 4K - Calming anxiety reduction' from the channel MindfulPeace.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
